    This project called "update-fstab" is a Python script that makes use of a local config, in
    which different variables are set up. You can modify those at your pleasure to tell `update-fstab'
    which files to modify, where to create the backup and logs and under what name. It updates your fstab
    file accordingly to your specifications.

